column1: Does your employer provide mental health benefits as part of healthcare coverage?
column2: Do you know the options for mental health care available under your employer-provided coverage?
column3: Does your employer offer resources to learn more about mental health concerns and options for seeking help?
column4: If a mental health issue prompted you to request a medical leave from work, asking for that leave would be:
column5: Do you think that discussing a mental health disorder with your employer would have negative consequences?
column6: Do you think that discussing a physical health issue with your employer would have negative consequences?
column7: Do you feel that your employer takes mental health as seriously as physical health?
column8: Have you heard of or observed negative consequences for co-workers who have been open about mental health issues in your workplace?
column10: Have your previous employers provided mental health benefits?
column11: Were you aware of the options for mental health care provided by your previous employers?
column12: Did your previous employers ever formally discuss mental health (as part of a wellness campaign or other official communication)?
column13: Was your anonymity protected if you chose to take advantage of mental health or substance abuse treatment resources with previous employers?
column14: Do you think that discussing a mental health disorder with previous employers would have negative consequences?
column15: Would you have been willing to discuss a mental health issue with your direct supervisor(s)?
column16: Did you feel that your previous employers took mental health as seriously as physical health?
column17: Did you hear of or observe negative consequences for co-workers with mental health issues in your previous workplaces?
column18: Would you bring up a mental health issue with a potential employer in an interview?
column19: Do you feel that being identified as a person with a mental health issue would hurt your career?
column20: Do you think that team members/co-workers would view you more negatively if they knew you suffered from a mental health issue?
column21: How willing would you be to share with friends and family that you have a mental illness?
column22: Have you observed or experienced an unsupportive or badly handled response to a mental health issue in your current or previous workplace?
column23: Do you have a family history of mental illness?
column24: Have you had a mental health disorder in the past?
column25: Do you currently have a mental health disorder?
column26: Have you been diagnosed with a mental health condition by a medical professional?
column27: Have you ever sought treatment for a mental health issue from a mental health professional?
column28: If you have a mental health issue, do you feel that it interferes with your work when being treated effectively?
column29: If you have a mental health issue, do you feel that it interferes with your work when NOT being treated effectively?
column31: What country do you live in?
column32: What country do you work in?
